Description:
Product Description

Felicity 80A/48V Charge Controller Brief introduction of Felicity 80A 12V/24V/48V Charge Controller: An MPPT( Maximum Power Point Tracking ), or maximum power point tracker is an electronic DC to DC converter that optimizes the match between the solar array (PV panels), and the battery bank or utility grid. To put it simply, they convert a higher voltage DC output from solar panels (and a few wind generators) down to the lower voltage needed to charge batteries. Compared to conventional PWM controller, MPPT technology increases the charge efficiency up to 20% and potentially decrease the power of solar array needed. 120A MPPT Solar Charge Controller Regulator With LCD Display, Maximum charging current up to 60A,Integrated intelligent slot compatible with SNMP/MODBUS communication.

Description:
Product Description

PLS-DF06 Pulmos Smart Door Lock This Pulmos smart door lock (PLS-DF06) is a newly designed smart door lock with surveillance camera. Think of it as that smart device with dual features of  home security and door lock. Its integrated design makes it really easy to install and the buttons for operation are placed right in front of the device. The password lock is fully automatic and can also be locked and unlocked remotely.  Other features include:
  • Easy Users management
  • Quick addition and delete  of unwanted user account,
  • Fingerprint & passwords
  • Powered by 4AA alkaline batteries
  • Three unlocking modes: password, smart card and Mechanical key
  • No computer process required
  • Auto alert at low voltage
The device allows for card use and password unlocks while allowing for easy password management and (or) reset. It is suitable for home use or commercial purposes.

Description:
Product Description

The LifeSmart window sensor works to detect and report opening and closing of doors and windows. This unique feature makes it ideal for use in home care, access control and home security.  The  LifeSmart window sensor is a simple-to-install door/window sensor combined with magnetic sensor and vibrating sensor. The LifeSmart’s CUBE Door/window Sensor can send a notification through your Life Smart App when the door/window is detected open. It can also be used to trigger events with other smart devices, like taking a snapshot with your Smart Home Wi-Fi Camera of whoever enters your house. This device is equipped with a vibration sensor that notifies  you when someone tries to break-in.  It is also a CUBE Clicker. One simple click can trigger a series of actions of the smart devices. Description:
Product Description

Microtek Pure Sine Wave Inverter 2.3KVA Microtek Inverter 2.3KVA is an Indian brand of inverters that was founded in 1986. This Inverter uses the latest in  MPPT/PWM algorithm to produce a smooth pure sine wave output, that allows the device to run without a continuous humming or buzzing sound. This amazing feature helps to create a safer and noiseless inverter solution. Also, this Pure Sine-Wave Inverter, designed with bigger transformers, the Microtek pure sine wave Inverter 2.3KVA can provide better performance for a longer period of time. It provides an affordable and alternative power solution for homes and small businesses. Microtek Inverter 2.3KVA possesses a micro-controller-based intelligent control design and displays indicators for faults and status. Furthermore, users enjoy long backups and extra protection for electronic devices from sudden power cuts. Microtek pure sine wave inverter-2.3KVA is easily serviceable and manageable, with its intelligent control design and indicators. Therefore, the output wave-form is a sine-wave with very low harmonic distortion and clean power like utility-supplied electricity—essential for your expensive equipment. It prevents crashes in computers, weird print outs and glitches in computer monitors. In conclusion, it saves electricity on charging, and clocks and audio equipment will behave much better on a pure sine wave. Features include:
  • Highly Efficient PWM Charging ensures More Battery Life and Improved Solar System Performance.
  • Automatically recognizes Day & Night.
  • Mosfet Switching System.
  • Micro Controller-based design.
  • Priority Load Sharing through Solar during the daytime, thereby saving your mains electricity.
  • Functions independently as a Solar Charge Controller when the front Switch is in Off Position.
  • Compatible with all types of Batteries: SMF/Flat Plate/Tubular.

Name: GNT-5313AB Genata PoE Splitter
Short description: GNT-5313AB Genata PoE Splitter is an economical and practical, high-performance, and high-reliability PoE remote power receiving device based on the IEEE 802.3af standard, which can separate power and data signals
Description:
Product Description

GNT-5313AB Genata PoE Splitter GNT-5313AB Genata PoE Splitter is an economical and practical, high-performance, and high-reliability PoE remote power receiving device based on the IEEE 802.3af standard, which can separate power and data signals transmitted through network cables. It’s a PoE Synthesizer separator Converter cable connector for CCTV systems. Consider it a power supply equipment that complies with the IEEE 802.3af standard configured to provide data and power for network equipment that does not support PoE. GNT-5313AB Genata PoE Splitter; PoE Synthesizer separator Converter is widely used in WiFi Access Points, IP CCTV Cameras, security, video & network cameras. It’s a network cabling connector that is suitable for wireless LAN (WLAN) network monitoring. Easy to install and use, you can quickly connect the cable with the supplied wiring harness. Made of high-quality abs material, sturdy and durable. It allows you to save on wiring costs and is suitable for network monitoring systems, network-integrated wiring. PoE Splitter splits a PoE signal into a 12VDC power and 10/100Mbps ethernet data source. Moreover, this device allows you to run ethernet cables from a POE Switch over long distances. It then splits the PoE signal into a separate data signal and 12Vdc power sources in order to run a non-PoE devices. In addition, you’d also find it has short-circuit protection, over-temperature protection that helps in preventing the device from a surge. This Geneta POE Splitter device is available in our Lekki and Ikeja office.

GNT-2910AB Genata Optical Fiber Module GNT-2910AB Genata Fiber Optical Module or SFP Optical fiber module is a high performance, cost-effective module that features a duplex SC optic interface . Standard AC coupled CML for high speed signal and LVTTL and monitor signals. The receiver section uses a PIN receiver and transmitter. The signal uses a 1310 nm FP laser, up to 14dB link budge, giving this module a 1000 base Ethernet 3km application. This SFP Optical Module is a hot-pluggable network interface module used for both telecommunication and data communications applications. An electrical interface on the side that connects to the inside of the system and an optical interface on the other side that connects to the various devices through a fiber optic cable. This optical fiber module also functions as a photoelectric converter that converts the electrical signal into light and vice versa. In conclusion, Optical modules are deployed to update the communication networks and data center networks for efficient traffic management with higher speeds. Optical networks are the backbone for mobile communication network. With growing demand for reliable and high speed mobile communication, optical transceivers are increasingly being used for the communication network infrastructure and to make your optical network thrive significantly.

Product Description

GNT-P1006G6 Genata 4 Port PoE Extender Switch GNT-P1006G6 Genata 4 Port PoE Extender Switch has the new PoE AI watchdog functionality. It is powered with automatic detection and is able to restart the device when there’s a power failure. It has a PoE power flashing light indicator to indicate the power status. The Genata 4 Port PoE Extender Switch supports IEEE 802.3 af/at. The single power maximum output power is 60W and can be used for high power devices such as PTZ Camera. Doubles the maximum connection distance between PoE source and device from 100 m (328 ft.) to 200 m (656 ft.). This PoE Extender was designed to be as easy as possible to set up and use. All it takes to have it up and running is to connect its “PoE In” port to your PoE injector or PoE switch and to connect the “PoE Out” ports to the PoE devices you want to connect (e.g., a VoIP phone and a PoE network camera). Name: GNT-6FP31 Genata Outdoor POE Extender
Short description: GNT-6FP31 Genata Outdoor POE Extender offers a smart and easy-to-install solution for extending the range of your network – with no additional power supply. Without being restricted by the 100m
Description:
Product Description

GNT-6FP31 Genata Outdoor POE Extender offers a smart and easy-to-install solution for extending the range of your network – with no additional power supply. Without being restricted by the 100m (328ft.) limit for Ethernet cables, power over ethernet devices can be installed at greater distances. Simply connect GNT-6FP31 Genata Outdoor POE Extender in-line with the CAT5e or CAT6 cable and power is forwarded to your Axis network video product. has an isolation transformer which protects the circuit and electrical equipment. The device has matching PoE synthesizer separation converter which makes it suitable for use in multiple scenarios. GNT-6FP31 Genata Outdoor PoE Extender supports PoE, and it is both IEEE 802.3af, IEEE 802.3at and High PoE 60 W compatible. With its rugged, IP66/IP67 -rated enclosure, GNT-6FP31 withstands harsh environmental conditions and challenging temperatures. It supports cascades 4 times and has a maximum transmission distance of 130m. Range depends on the power required so depending on midspan and camera type the connection can in total be between 200-400 meters (656-1312 ft.) It is more convenient, safer and highly cost effective, for this reason, half of the network cables can be saved on the project. Other features include:
DATA SHEET
Bandwidth 0.6Gbps.
Mac Address 2K
Max transmission distance 130m
Support IEEE 802.3af/at/bt protocol
Power input POE Powered
Other Fuction support cascade 4 times
Size 156*92*42mm

Name: Pulmos Mifare Hotel lock smart card
Short description: The Pulmos Mifare Hotel lock smart card is a contactless proximity Mifare card. It is a programable card for a single room in the hotel but also allows multi-use memory,
Description:
Product Description

The Pulmos Mifare Hotel lock smart card is a contactless proximity Mifare card. It is a programable card for a single room in the hotel but also allows multi-use memory, which means that it can hold multiple access. Each card can be reprogrammed several thousand times with a variety of information (access to different places, personal data. If a card is lost, it can be cancelled in the hotel software immediately. The Pulmos Mifare Hotel lock smart card is normally blank (white), or it can be customized according to owner’s choice. Product features:
  • Good anti-counterfeiting, and high confidentiality
  • One Hotel key card can be used for multiple access
  • It is suitable for enterprises, hotels, campuses, smart communities, and various multi-system integration occasions that require the implementation of a card.
  • It is also ideal for financial institutions and other places that need high system security.
  • MIFARE1 card is generally suitable for star hotels or units that require card functions due to its high security, large capacity, independent encryption.
MIFARE hotel locks rooms are currently the world’s most used. It has the most mature technology, the most stable performance, and the most significant memory capacity of an inductive smart IC card.The card is widely used in the Mifare key card door locks for hotel rooms. Suitable for mid-to-high-end hotels or large-scale intelligent hotels that truly need to implement the “One Card System” function.

Description:
Product Description

K-Star Inverter Battery 200AH-12V The K-Star Inverter Battery 200AH/12V valve-regulated lead-acid battery can prevent air from being absorbed into it. At the same time, it also can protect the battery from damage caused by gas emitting in the period of recharging. Also, there is no emission of acid mist and electrolyte when the sealed battery is in floating condition. Its handle design makes it easy for carrying and easy access during Transportation. It also has a lifespan of 5 years. Meanwhile, the patented battery tray can match with the battery and it can protect it from the harm of electrolyte leakage. It belongs to the class of AGM (Absorbed Glass Mat). In addition, K-Star Inverter Battery 200AH/12V is suitable for Power Backup, Uninterruptible Power Supply (UPS), and Motorized Wheel Chair, and other DC applications. Products features are:
  • Robust tabular with high pressure die casted spine-resulting low rate of sine collision.
  • Ceramic vent plugs-special ceramic vent plugs for controlled Acid fumes.
  • Unique negative paste recipe for high charge acceptance.
  • Consistent backup throughout life.
  • Excellent behaviour in PSOC condition.
  • Low self-discharge.
  • Excellent performance on deep cyclic application.
  • High design and service life.
  • Low chance of Acid stratification.
  • Available in factory charged condition for ready to use.
